Fundings and special thanks :
-----------------------------

Development of lcmm was part of the ANR-funded project MOBIDYQ, grant #2010 PRSP 006 01, the IRESP-funded project MULTIPLE, grant #AAP12CanBio16, the ANR-funded project DyMES, grant ANR-18-CE36-0004-01.

The authors thank Raphael Peter for his suggestion to add a parallel version of gridsearch.

The authors also thank Samy Youbi for his help with the vignettes, and Sasha Cuau for her help on posterior functions predictClass, predictRE and summaryplot.

The authors finally thank the R-core team for their constant help. 

